Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION for cases that are corrected and resubmitted
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time for Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to be followed by Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE after Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time it takes Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to be followed by Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for cases with Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to reach Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and Request Payment for cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE that are successfully resubmitted and approved
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER for cases that involve budget owner approval after rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time it takes for cases with Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to be finalized with Payment Handled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR for cases that require supervisor approval after rejection
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER to identify patterns leading to rejections by pre-approver
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
